This is an Online Pizza Shop I developed in Php and Mysql to practically implement and understand MVC design Pattern
Make sure Apache and Sql server are in running status to run this code
The Website allows us to use it as an admin or a student (customer)
Admin can add a new size, toppigs, set the status of order etc
Student can order the pizza of availble size and toppings to thier room.no

Its a backend application ,So didnt work much on the display. 


If error occurs, try changing the value of $app_path (in header.php in veiw file) to the foldername where this project runs.
